data.description:
Welcome to your beautiful new home, complete with a cozy fireplace! You'll absolutely love its amazing location, right across from the greenbelt. It's perfect for taking the kids to play or taking your furry friends for a walk. Inside, you'll find a stunning kitchen with gorgeous Mocha cabinets, granite counters, and a convenient breakfast bar. The stainless steel range, dishwasher, and built-in microwave are all ready to assist you in your culinary adventures. Plus, there's an interior laundry room for added convenience. The living room features lovely wood laminate flooring and a warm, inviting fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings with loved ones. The family room, kitchen, and baths boast stylish porcelain tile throughout, and both bathrooms showcase elegant granite counters. And And don't forget about the custom walk-in closet in the primary bedroom, which offers ample space for all your wardrobe needs.

Outside, you'll discover a covered patio, perfect for relaxing or hosting outdoor gatherings. The low maintenance yard means less time spent on upkeep, and the RV gate provides added convenience. And of course, the sparkling blue pool is ideal for cooling off during those warm Arizona summers. Best of all, there's no HOA to worry about!

This home is conveniently located near ASU West, the I-17 freeway, shopping, and dining. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home with a cozy fireplace. Take a look before it's too late!
